  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Metro Green Job  - Energy efficiency and waste handling</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project s main target is to explore the possibility to make waste handling and energy consumption in the company safer and more environmental friendly whereby create more jobs. The initial feasibility study will give an overview of the waste magnitude and energy consumption in the 16 Metro stores in Zimbabwe and estimate the need for investments and system improvements necessary for Metro to be a safer workplace for more employees, and a more energy efficient company.</narrative>
  </description>
